t_A = \sqrt{2}\cdot\dfrac{bc}{b+c}
\triangle BDF \sim \triangle DCE \; \implies \; \frac{s}{c-s} = \frac{b-s}{s} \; \implies \; \frac{b c}{b+c} = s = \frac{t}{\sqrt{2}} \; \implies \; t = \sqrt{2}\frac{bc}{b+c}
\frac{AD}{c}=\frac{b}{\sqrt{b^2+c^2}}
